title: El Rincon Natural
description: Spanish-speaking health food shop at the lower end of Calle Blas Infante. Offering dried goods, herbal remedies, some vegetarian chilled goods such as veggie burgers and tofu, some alternative health books, supplements, toiletries, precious stones and jewelery. Special orders can be requested. Complementary therapies offered include kinesiology, sports massage, auricular acupuncture, Bach Flower, and others.
streetAddress: Calle Blas Infante,  23, Arroyo de la Miel, Malaga
